  "instructions": [
    "season the chicken breast with salt, cumin, paprika, and black pepper.",
    "heat the olive oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "add the minced onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute.",
    "add the flour and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "add the concentrated tomato puree, chilli sauce, and water. stir to combine.",
    "bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 10 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "add the chicken breast to the pan and cook for an additional 12-15 minutes, or until cooked through.",
    "dust with flour before serving."
